{"tid":2404464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"期待左好耐既盤菜，食剩後氣味似經血！","createTime":"2021-02-11T17:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T17:26:52.000Z","uid":292741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c92e185c5bc7e081b9119d0eeef335c496c7402","tid":2404464,"uid":292741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"幾年前食過，印象中唔好食。<br />\n<br />\n今年見到sell 到咁恆，又忘記左咩味，決定多試次。<br />\n<br />\n特登搵間老字號，貴少少，食好d ，點知食落去件件一樣味，但始終d汁都好餸飯，成程都食得幾開胃，幾飽下。<br />\n<br />\n食既時候唔覺，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">之後就黎料。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">食剩一半，放係大廳，d 菜混和蘿蔔海鮮，搞到成屋都係腥味，成兜野黑紅色，愈諗愈唔對路，愈聞愈似經味。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地係去親戚屋企食，親戚細食，比左我媽攞食剩既番去。<br />\n<br />\n我叫佢揼撚柒左佢啦，但最後浪費唔落手。攞上的士，e家成車都係個陣味。的士開得快，食得又飽，越聞越想嘔。"},{"pid":"b892c0234b556ac223f3abb7d3854555d3bc2ce6","tid":2404464,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"7dba88b0bcdf5a4a2628979d82923f26ffe8e0ad","tid":2404464,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"經血係咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1fa70a406e9668e7508d3dae72265bfe84948","tid":2404464,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dba88b0bcdf5a4a2628979d82923f26ffe8e0ad","tid":2404464,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"經血係咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"青頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1f23ebb6102837309290c8778ead6e9a1b767b","tid":2404464,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece1fa70a406e9668e7508d3dae72265bfe84948","tid":2404464,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dba88b0bcdf5a4a2628979d82923f26ffe8e0ad","tid":2404464,"uid":67553,"like":0